00:39:11,160 --> 00:39:13,040
ask you to put in a word
with Mr. Xiang for me.

866
00:39:13,440 --> 00:39:14,400
Isn't he downstairs right now?

867
00:39:15,080 --> 00:39:16,160
He is.

868
00:39:16,200 --> 00:39:17,360
But for this,

869
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:19,520
I still need you to bring it up for me.

870
00:39:20,480 --> 00:39:21,560
Must be pretty important

871
00:39:21,560 --> 00:39:23,320
if you need me to say it for you.

872
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:26,120
I want to learn photography
from Mr. Xiang.

873
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:28,080
You want to learn photography?

874
00:39:28,240 --> 00:39:29,280
What's wrong with that?

875
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:30,800
Good grief.

876
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:31,480
Am I not allowed?

877
00:39:31,480 --> 00:39:32,440
I didn't say that.

878
00:39:33,080 --> 00:39:34,040
It's just,

879
00:39:34,040 --> 00:39:35,400
why do both of you
want to learn photography?

880
00:39:35,400 --> 00:39:36,280
Both of us?

881
00:39:38,080 --> 00:39:38,720
Oh,

882
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,240
Shen Taotao.

883
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:42,960
I'm nothing like her.

884
00:39:43,600 --> 00:39:45,240
I genuinely

885
00:39:45,240 --> 00:39:46,160
just want to learn photography.

886
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:48,280
Sure, sure, pure motives.

887
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,480
Very pure, good.

888
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:50,760
Alright, when I go downstairs,

889
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:52,240
I'll let him know

890
00:39:52,240 --> 00:39:54,000
how badly you want to learn photography.

891
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:54,560
Sound good?

892
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:55,800
Yes.

893
00:39:56,840 --> 00:39:57,480
Thank you, Mentor.

894
00:39:57,600 --> 00:39:58,280
No problem.

895
00:40:02,240 --> 00:40:02,880
Nice place.

896
00:40:05,560 --> 00:40:06,000
Hey.

897
00:40:09,280 --> 00:40:10,480
You can say what you really came to say.

898
00:40:11,120 --> 00:40:15,120
Just don't get upset when I do.

899
00:40:15,160 --> 00:40:18,360
If you don't say it,
then I'll get upset.

900
00:40:21,240 --> 00:40:22,320
Careful!

901
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:23,000
I'm fine.

902
00:40:26,560 --> 00:40:27,560
It's just,

903
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:30,520
I have this feeling…

904
00:40:34,040 --> 00:40:35,040
Stringing this out, really?

905
00:40:35,040 --> 00:40:35,920
What feeling?

906
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:40,080
Back at your place just now,

907
00:40:40,480 --> 00:40:41,920
watching Mr. Xiang,

908
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:43,880
the way he talked

909
00:40:43,880 --> 00:40:45,360
and carried himself…

910
00:40:47,080 --> 00:40:47,880
I don't know why,

911
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:49,920
but he felt like the head of the family.

912
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:51,480
That's not surprising.

913
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:53,560
Anyone who's ever been to my house

914
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:54,840
says the same thing.

915
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:57,240
After all these years,

916
00:40:57,680 --> 00:40:59,240
he's been looking after my mom and me.

917
00:40:59,400 --> 00:41:00,160
My mom and I

918
00:41:00,160 --> 00:41:01,880
already see him as family.

919
00:41:02,200 --> 00:41:03,320
It's completely normal.

920
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:06,680
So you must trust him completely.

921
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:07,600
Of course.

922
00:41:07,920 --> 00:41:08,920
He'd never hurt me.

923
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,520
No wonder.

924
00:41:19,640 --> 00:41:20,360
Only he could've

925
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:22,640
been trying to set you up
with Shen Taotao.

926
00:41:22,640 --> 00:41:24,040
Stop right there.

927
00:41:24,200 --> 00:41:25,520
Don't mix things up.
Stop talking nonsense.

928
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:27,680
Report complete, Mentor.

929
00:41:27,680 --> 00:41:28,520
Requesting permission to leave.

930
00:41:28,560 --> 00:41:29,360
Leave? Seriously?

931
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:30,320
You haven't even eaten.

932
00:41:30,320 --> 00:41:32,600
Gonna get myself a camera ASAP.

933
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:34,680
I'm counting on you
to talk to Mr. Xiang for me.

934
00:41:35,120 --> 00:41:35,600
Bye!

935
00:41:35,600 --> 00:41:36,400
Hey, wait!

936
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:45,880
Tao,

937
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,080
are we really okay

938
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:48,480
doing this?

939
00:41:51,360 --> 00:41:52,680
What could happen?

940
00:41:53,080 --> 00:41:54,800
I've done this plenty of times.

941
00:41:55,680 --> 00:41:56,680
When we land,

942
00:41:57,040 --> 00:41:58,920
put those bags and jewelry

943
00:41:58,920 --> 00:42:00,480
in your carry-on.

944
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:02,400
After we get off the plane,

945
00:42:02,400 --> 00:42:03,680
wait in the restroom for a while.

946
00:42:04,160 --> 00:42:06,200
We'll go through
after all the passengers are gone.

947
00:42:07,640 --> 00:42:09,120
We won't get checked, right?

948
00:42:09,320 --> 00:42:10,440
No.

949
00:42:11,080 --> 00:42:12,120
We're flight attendants.

950
00:42:12,120 --> 00:42:13,040
We fly every day.

951
00:42:13,160 --> 00:42:14,640
The customs officers know us.

952
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:15,720
Xi'e,

953
00:42:16,680 --> 00:42:19,240
I only brought you in
because you said you needed money.

954
00:42:19,920 --> 00:42:21,440
And now you're getting cold feet?

955
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:24,200
Yeah,

956
00:42:24,880 --> 00:42:26,200
there's risk

957
00:42:26,200 --> 00:42:27,360
in making money like this.

958
00:42:28,080 --> 00:42:29,800
But it's way faster

959
00:42:29,800 --> 00:42:31,560
than grinding away and saving up.

960
00:42:35,040 --> 00:42:36,160
You're right, Tao.

961
00:42:37,640 --> 00:42:38,400
I'm in.

962
00:42:40,560 --> 00:42:41,400
Bye. Take care.

963
00:42:41,400 --> 00:42:42,320
- Bye, take care. - Bye.

964
00:42:42,320 --> 00:42:43,480
Hope to see you on board again.

965
00:42:43,560 --> 00:42:44,520
Bye. Take care.

966
00:42:45,840 --> 00:42:47,160
- Take care. - Take care.

967
00:42:50,120 --> 00:42:51,040
- Bye. - Bye.

968
00:42:51,040 --> 00:42:52,040
Bye. Good work today.

969
00:42:52,040 --> 00:42:52,800
Bye, Tao.

970
00:42:52,800 --> 00:42:53,800
Good work. Bye.

971
00:42:53,800 --> 00:42:55,200
We'll get going then. Bye.

972
00:42:55,200 --> 00:42:55,840
Bye.

973
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:37,360
♪There's a place of simple,
everyday warmth♪

974
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:45,000
♪A door left open
for the wandering soul♪

975
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:52,440
♪A humble table still warm with love♪

976
00:43:52,680 --> 00:43:56,320
♪After you've tasted every high and low♪

977
00:43:56,600 --> 00:44:00,240
♪Come home, I'll keep you warm♪

978
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:07,680
♪Where the days begin and end♪

979
00:44:08,440 --> 00:44:15,320
♪A light still on for the ones
who've lost their way♪

980
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:22,680
♪An embrace waiting just for you♪

981
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:26,680
♪Through every passing season♪

982
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:30,480
♪Even if you return with nothing at all♪

983
00:44:31,120 --> 00:44:34,600
♪Turn around and look♪

984
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:38,600
♪That door's still open♪

985
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:42,440
♪A light still burning♪

986
00:44:42,520 --> 00:44:46,240
♪Waiting there for you♪

987
00:44:46,400 --> 00:44:49,920
♪Turn around and look♪

988
00:44:50,160 --> 00:44:53,960
♪Someone's still waiting♪

989
00:44:54,160 --> 00:44:57,760
♪Watching the dusk settle in♪

990
00:44:57,840 --> 00:45:01,560
♪Waiting for the break of dawn♪

991
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:07,000
♪It's always there♪
